These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, juice, mirinda, lemonade
4 different games are played: scrabble, monopoly, go, canasta
City: san-francisco, liverpool, hannover, berlin
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, surfing, volleyball, skateboarding
1. the person playing monopoly is the person drinking water##1
2. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the person traveling to hannover is the person playing scrabble##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
5. the person playing go is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
6. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
7. the person playing monopoly is the person who's sport is basketball##1
8. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
9. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage         | water  | lemonade  | juice | mirinda |
| Game           | monopoly | scrabble | canasta  | go  |
| City   | berlin       | hannover      | san-francisco | liverpool      |
| Sport           | basketball          | surfing     | volleyball    | skateboarding     |

