.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, dancing, photography, video-games
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, orchid, dahlia, aconite
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, zombie, drama, disaster
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, december, july, november
1. the person who growslily is on the far right##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
5. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
6. the person who's hobby is photography is the person watching drama movies##1
7. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
8. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
9. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby      | photography     | writing       | dancing | video-games        |
| Flower          | aconite     | orchid       | dahlia   | lily   |
| Movie-Genre   | drama      | zombie       | disaster     | satire    |
| Birthday         | july | november | september | december |

