.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, cabbage, lime, banana
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, biathlon, tennis, lacrosse
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, daisy, iris, bellflower
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, disco, d&b, rock
 1. the person eating banana is the fan of rock##1
 2. the person eating lime is on the far right##1
 3. the person who growsiris is on the far right##1
 4. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
 5. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 6. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
 7. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 8. the person eating lime is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 9. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the fan of rock##1
10. the person eating lime is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| Food      | cabbage | broccoli       | banana        | lime        |
| Sport           | biathlon   | tennis | swimming   | lacrosse |
| Flower   | balloon-flower     | daisy    | bellflower | iris        |
| Music-Genre           | d&b         | salsa  | rock       | disco         |

