There are 4 different favourite colors: white, black, fuchsia, lilac
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, ritmeester, chaman, siglo
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far left##1
2. the cain-smoker is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
3. the ritmeester-smoker is on the far left##1
4. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who likes white##1
5. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
6. the siglo-smoker is the person who likes fuchsia##1
7. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
8. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
9. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Flower           | marigold  | amaryllis    | sunflower | aconite |
| Birthday   | january      | february    | december         | october    |
| Color   | black   | white     | fuchsia          | lilac      |
