.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-6::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, ship, boat, tram
City: berlin, prague, marseilles, edinburgh
House: farmhouse, futuristic, modern, cape-cod
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, mirinda, fanta, lemonade
 1. the person driving the boat is the farmhouse house##1
 2. the person driving the scooter is the futuristic house##1
 3. the person traveling to berlin is the farmhouse house##1
 4. the person drinking fanta is the person driving the scooter##1
 5. the modern house is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 6. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 7. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 8. the farmhouse house is on the right of the modern house##1
 9. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far left##1
10. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Transport          | scooter  | tram | boat     | ship |
| City           | marseilles  | edinburgh      | berlin | prague    |
| House   | futuristic | modern  | farmhouse    | cape-cod  |
| Beverage           | fanta   | lemonade       | coffee       | mirinda      |

