 7. the cape-cod house is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 8. the person who likes chestnut is on the far left##1
 9. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person who likes black##1
10. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
