There are 4 different favourite colors: pink, yellow, blue, coral
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the fan of rock##1
2. the owner of the pony is the fan of salsa##1
3. the fan of jazz is on the left of the fan of metal##1
4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
5. the fan of salsa is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
6. the fan of jazz is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person who likes pink##1
8. the person who likes blue is the owner of the goat##1
9. the person who likes coral is the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |     4      |
| Pet      | pony      | goat         | rat        | goldfish      |
| Hobby           | skydiving | camping | rock-climbing  | video-games  |
| Music-Genre   | salsa    | jazz     | metal | rock     |
| Color     | pink        | blue     | yellow     | coral |

